snippet.title: Pro Philosopher 2: Announce Teaser
snippet.description:
Pro Philosopher 2: Governments and Grievances is coming to Steam in 2024! Take on famous political philosophers in a series of comical interactive debates, change their minds, and change the world!
Wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2120070/Pro_Philosopher_2_Governments__Grievances/
